  "detailed_description": "<strong>Five Ronin, destined for death.</strong> The only things they trust - their weapon and their speed.<br><br>Use your mouse and draw your line of attack to kill your enemies in endless arena combat.<br><br>Everything can be killed in one hit - including you.<br><br>How long can you survive?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983000/extras/a1496c0bd193edf65e61255e873d5f21.poster.avif?t=1653210414\" width=660 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983000/extras/a1496c0bd193edf65e61255e873d5f21.webm?t=1653210414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983000/extras/a1496c0bd193edf65e61255e873d5f21.mp4?t=1653210414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique mouse-based combat system<br></li><li> 5 characters, each with different playstyles<br></li><li> Frenetic combo system<br></li><li> Leaderboards to compete against your friends and the world<br></li><li> Achievements that force you to change up tactics<br></li><li> Drawing tablet support (enable from options)</li></ul>",
